                                    <td class="p-4">Deck of cards</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
                                    <td class="p-4 font-bold">140W-240W</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Gaming laptops, workstations</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Laptop at full speed + accessories</td>
                                    <td class="p-4">Smartphone-sized</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">The <strong>65W GaN charger</strong> is the current sweet spot — it charges most ultrabooks at full speed while remaining pocket-friendly. For B2B buyers and OEM brands, 65W also represents the best balance of performance, BOM cost, and retail price point.</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">WOWOHCOOL produces OEM/ODM GaN chargers from <strong>20W to 240W</strong>. Explore our <a href="/products/gan-charger" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange font-bold">GaN charger product line</a> for specifications and MOQ details.</p>
